'Candy meets .. Sheila E'

Candy Dulfer visits Sheila E in Los Angeles. They talk about their first encounter, Sheila's foundation, Prince, religion and of course music. First broadcasted by the NPS on October 14, 2007. This is a re-broadcast (2010-10-18). Some comments by Candy are in dutch, so I added some english subs.
